caption.title: Phylogeographic distribution of the DENV-2 Cosmopolitan Clade 1 genotype in the world.
caption.p: The virus clade had migrated to Sri Lanka from the South-East Asian region. The figure was generated using the map is available in the free software SPREAD [ 25], which is also available in Maps at CIA ( https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/images/home_world_map.jpg).
